snippet.title: Street Fighter 6 - Ed Update Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the Ed Update now in Street Fighter 6! Meet the boxer in World Tour, learn his psycho-powered moves for Avatar Battles in the Battle Hub, and put on the gloves yourself in Fighting Ground.

A few more quality-of-life updates and character balance changes have also made their way into the ring, so be sure to check them out.

https://streetfighter.com/6/

#Ed #StreetFighter6 #Capcom #StreetFighter
